Interface EventListener<T extends Event>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ErrorListener, RTCConnectionStateChangeEventListener, RTCDataChannel.BufferedAmountLowListener, RTCDataChannel.CloseListener, RTCDataChannel.ClosingListener, RTCDataChannel.MessageListener, RTCDataChannel.OpenListener, RTCDataChannelEventListener, RTCIceCandidateEventListener, RTCIceConnectionStateChangeEventListener, RTCIceGatheringStateChangeEventListener, RTCIdentityResultEventListener, RTCMediaElement.RTCMediaElementListener, RTCNegotiationNeededEventListener, RTCSignalingStateChangeEventListener, RTCTrackEventListener

    public interface EventListener<T extends Event>

    The EventListener interface represents an object that can handle an event dispatched by an EventTarget object.

    See Also:
    https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventListener
